# Claude Code — fully ignore. Includes per-project settings, installed-skill
# symlinks created by `npx skills add ...`, and the AI-config CLAUDE.md
# generated by `ng new --ai-config=claude`. Anything Claude Code needs from
# this repo should live in `skills/` (the source-of-truth skill folder).
.claude/

